data.description: Welcome to a charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with great potential. This residence is located in a desirable area and awaits your creative touch to transform it into a personalized haven. The spacious rooms, solid structure, and generous yard provide a perfect foundation for your ideas. With a little TLC, you can turn this property into a unique gem that reflects your style and aspirations. What's more, the seller is motivated to sell and is even willing to assist with covering closing costs, making this an even more enticing opportunity. Embrace the journey of making this house your dream home and seize the opportunity to create something truly special. Schedule your showing today!!
